general.gigTitle: design, develop and kickstart your ecommerce shopify website

sellerCard.oneLiner: Certified Shopify Expert, E Commerce Specialist
sellerCard.description:
With over a decade of experience in web development, I’ve had the privilege of helping clients worldwide bring their visions to life.

I specialize in creating high-conversion Shopify stores and delivering tailored development solutions to meet your unique needs.

Whether you’re looking to build a new website, resolve technical issues, or elevate the professional appeal of your existing Shopify website, I’m here to assist.

Let’s work together to make your project a success – feel free to reach out anytime!

description.content:
Please get in touch with me before ordering so we can go over the project details.


If you are new to Shopify I will guide you throughout the process. I will set up your store on development and install the theme that is most suitable to your product. I have developed stores including one product shops, one niche shop, multiple products and niches shop. I have been developing stunning stores for the last five years for clients around the world. 


Setup aesthetics will include:

  • Colors
  • Typography
  • Backgrounds


Pages setup will include:

  • Homepage
  • Collection page
  • Collection List
  • Blog
  • Product page
  • Cart page
  • Checkout
  • Contact form


Application/ Plugins

  • Customer contact platform
  • Order notification
  • Upsell application
  • Customer review application
  • any other application required by your business


Work Flow

  • You place an order
  • You provide me business needs, content and discuss work scope
  • Get your website up and running
  • Review
  • Launch your store

reviews.comment: Nas was very responsive and delivered the project on time, making all the changes I requested. The work on my Shopify store was good, but a bit more attention to detail would have really hit the mark. Overall, he went above and beyond in responsiveness and effort.
Nas is an expert with Shopify- they went above and beyond to help me set up a store from scratch. Amazing service and easy to work with!
Amazing to work with. Knowledgeable, professional, and above all patient. Cares about the quality of work! I will be back! Thank you Nas!
Very happy with a new theme, at a great price
